{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01An17fBJKqkXUGUy5HrYZug","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** Jakarta EE 10 (JSF/EJB/JPA on Open Liberty) -> Spring Boot 3.2.5 (REST/Spring Data JPA on embedded Tomcat)\n\n**High-level actions:**\n1. Replaced Jakarta EE platform dependency with Spring Boot starters\n2. Converted JSF-based UI controller to REST API controller\n3. Replaced EJB facade pattern with Spring Data JPA repository\n4. Migrated from Open Liberty server config to Spring Boot application.properties\n5. Updated Dockerfile from `liberty:run` to executable JAR\n\n**Overall outcome:** Success - all 12 smoke tests pass\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Jakarta EE dependencies with Spring Boot starters, changed packaging to jar\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/entity/Contact.java: Added @Table annotation\n- Dockerfile: Changed from liberty:run to java -jar with build step\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/AddressBookApplication.java: Spring Boot main class\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/repository/ContactRepository.java: Spring Data JPA repository\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/web/ContactController.java: REST controller (rewritten)\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring Boot configuration\n- smoke.py: Smoke tests for all CRUD operations\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/ejb/AbstractFacade.java: EJB pattern replaced by Spring Data\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/ejb/ContactFacade.java: Replaced by ContactRepository\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/web/util/JsfUtil.java: JSF-specific utility\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/addressbook/web/util/PaginationHelper.java: Replaced by Spring Data Pageable\n- src/main/webapp/ (all XHTML views, web.xml, faces-config.xml